7","tid":756493,"uid":4709,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T20:03:06.000Z","msg":"因為驚除緊衫果時撞親，罰黃牌其實係為左保護球員<br />\n<br />\n當年朗拿度用件波衫笠頭慶祝撞中門柱暈左之後加既新例黎"},{"pid":"f43cda3ff08849f320cbbb0c7b3bbe14edbb5497","tid":756493,"uid":155853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"319ec7c0aea3b23bb536846c82f9ba3ececa2dea","tid":756493,"uid":66433,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d99a286f576b36724ec68429a539412b3ad62597","tid":756493,"uid":185426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93812dca891e56b3d27ece55f5416b9210747684","tid":756493,"uid":53466,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:38:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T17:42:57.000Z","msg":"因為之前有條友除咗著唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T19:54:34.000Z","msg":"冇記錯係曼聯時期既科蘭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T20:06:45.000Z","msg":"開咗波仲未著得返，就咁拎住件衫撲波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4714b7f71d9a724df73453d566ba369db69b3e31","tid":756493,"uid":88763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T20:18:59.000Z","msg":"伊恩胡禮個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"443bd4bcdf12793382a27a39256f3a096e226902","tid":756493,"uid":189453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f43cda3ff08849f320cbbb0c7b3bbe14edbb5497","tid":756493,"uid":155853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"319ec7c0aea3b23bb536846c82f9ba3ececa2dea","tid":756493,"uid":66433,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d99a286f576b36724ec68429a539412b3ad62597","tid":756493,"uid":185426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T17:42:57.000Z","msg":"因為之前有條友除咗著唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T19:54:34.000Z","msg":"冇記錯係曼聯時期既科蘭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T20:06:45.000Z","msg":